- Pop a seedling bubble to see what color sprouts!
- Puzzles got you cracking your heads? Crack our new Egg bubble instead to see what's in store!
- Ability to log into multiple devices!
- Offline mode! Play on the go without an internet connection! (Just remember to connect back to the internet if you want to make a purchase from the App Store!)
- Bug fixes galore!

The world of Bubble Mania has never been more exciting!
Get ready for an adventure! We have thrilling NEW FEATURES for you to enjoy:

OVER 700 LEVELS: 700+ exciting bubble shooter puzzles with tons of new islands for you to discover!
NEW WEEKLY REWARDS: Unlock the fun with new Puzzle Levels, where you can collect hidden puzzle pieces to win dazzling treasures each week!
NEW TIERED LEADERBOARD: Compete with other players to see who is the best bubble shooter around in four prestigious tiers! Win prizes based on your weekly rank!
NEW FRIEND LEADERBOARD: Compare your progress with your friends to see who has collected the most puzzle pieces!
HALL OF FAME: Earn your place in Bubble Mania history by collecting the most Puzzle Pieces. Top puzzle piece hunters each week will be inducted into the Hall of Fame!

PERFORMANCE IMPROVEMENTS: We worked hard to make sure the game is in tip-top shape for this update! We’ve removed bugs and improved performance across the board!

Get ready to take your bubble shooting action to new heights…RAINBOW RUSH is about to begin! Show off your puzzle skills and prove that you have what it takes to reach the Castle in the Sky!

- New Weekly Events: Reach the end of the magical Rainbow Rush to become King of the Castle in the Sky and earn fantastic prizes!

- Global Leaderboard: Think you have what it takes to be the top ruler? Climb the Rainbow to earn crowns and see how your total stacks up against other skilled puzzlers throughout the world!

- Friend Leaderboard: Traveling over rainbows is more fun with good company! Compare progress with friends to see who has earned the most crowns!

- Over 800 Levels: Treat yourself to 800+ exciting levels of bubble shooter puzzles!

- Bug Fixes and Performance Improvements: We worked hard to get the game in top-notch shape for this update! The Rainbow’s light cleared away lots of bugs, and we’ve improved performance across the board!
